{"tid":2128320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外資銀行正拒絕香港官員賬戶 陳智思賬戶被關","createTime":"2020-07-28T01:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T02:13:06.000Z","uid":48973,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a141473b0192fd3fd4516b172545fade2b166b","tid":2128320,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》報導，行政會議召集人陳智思表示，外資銀行正在拒絕香港一些高級官員的賬戶。報道指，在頒布港區國家安全法之前，一間美國銀行關閉了陳智思的賬戶並於「最近」退還了錢款；陳智思未說明是哪間銀行。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述陳智思指，一些高級官員面臨類似的問題，陳智思又稱，美國的《香港自治法》將導致銀行在與當地官員打交道時更加「謹慎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1595897986336&amp;issue=20200728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1595897986336%26issue%3D20200728&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=da9ec44b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1595897986336&amp;issue=20200728</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c194a2b860e697d7b2ebc2df341d430ae7922b","tid":2128320,"uid":21493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"黑警係我哋仇人 黑警日日鬧事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2128286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2128286</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n重有3萬<br />\n<br />\n麻煩睇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推!!! 3萬thx"},{"pid":"e7b01f2e2fdbe0ed591f5eb3e5cdf3919abffe2c","tid":2128320,"uid":8745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"用國安法拉晒d美資銀行banker<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class